author: Corridor Crew
description:
The CGI baby in 2025, The Fantastic Four: First Steps, has gotten quite a bit of criticism for looking unrealistic. But considering the more than 150 CGI shots in which the Digital Domain team had to combine footage from 30 different babies into a single, consistent character, it's not really that bad!

Did it pull you out of the movie?
title: The Fantastic 4 CGI Baby
